              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Charged particles emitted by the scattering",
                "target were detected by the large area Si multi-",
                "detector system LEDA. Each sector consisted of 16",
                "strips with a thickness of 300 mum, an angular",
                "coverage of 42 degree and a total active area of",
                "45.9 cm**2."
